{"tid":1420502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"著住裝備就代表全部抗爭者","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T05:56:58.000Z","uid":237163,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e396484d500898dc207a381cc0e8c9c630869a21","tid":1420502,"uid":237163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:49:42.000Z","msg":"唔該大家，著住黑衫，戴住口罩，著埋其他gear ，就係代表所有抗爭者，代表人地點睇成個運動。<br />\n<br />\n我地diu 黑警無紀律，我地自己就要有紀律，所以要有禮貌！有禮貌！有禮貌！<br />\n<br />\n特別係有d街坊，唔知咁多規矩，走去影相，大家唔駛下下惡形惡相。<br />\n<br />\n講句：唔好意思，我地唔方便俾人影相，真係唔好意思，多謝你地既支持<br />\n<br />\n我知有時氣氛緊張大家會燥，但唔該大家控制自己情緒。"},{"pid":"5fbfc3963606dde84dff9fc7677472c7de616764","tid":1420502,"uid":237163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2d16191cc0e1686705eb5d9f7c396c6599d3a372","tid":1420502,"uid":17607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:14:38.000Z","msg":"PPPP"},{"pid":"c963fbe2d747adc6e52336885df1376233e71a5f","tid":1420502,"uid":90392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"同意, 唔洗第一句就兇, <br />\n對方表明立場係腦殘藍屍先屌柒佢都未遲"},{"pid":"76faaa0dc82c40f69e5fff55c5a9b68f32ca68d0","tid":1420502,"uid":193125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:57:25.000Z","msg":"表現有禮貌 先可以展現我們比狗優勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12a0b1f6aaa0618c134485c6652dbdc5627ed37","tid":1420502,"uid":43824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:55:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12778d9317d367b0ca0d331e06d11ef2d623375f","tid":1420502,"uid":104086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:56:58.000Z","msg":"同意 <br />\n我哋話得警察着起套制服就代表警隊<br />\n我哋其實都同樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}